General.Name: Radiant Logistics Inc
General.Description: Radiant Logistics, Inc., operates as a third-party logistics company, provides technology-enabled global transportation and value-added logistics solutions primarily in the United States and Canada. The company offers domestic, international air, and ocean freight forwarding services; and freight brokerage services, including truckload and intermodal services. It also provides logistics and supply chain services, including MM&D, CHB, and GTM services, as well as heavyweight and small package air services. In addition, the company offers air network services. It serves aviation and automotive, electronics and high tech, furniture and home furnishings, hospitality and gaming, humanitarian/NGO, industrial farming, and manufacturing and consumer goods; medical, healthcare, and pharmaceuticals; military and government; oil, gas, and energy; residential and white glove; retail, textile, apparel, and accessories; and trade shows, events, and advertising, as well as sporting goods industries. Radiant Logistics, Inc. was incorporated in 2001 and is headquartered in Renton, Washington.
